Package: template
Title: Generic template for research projects structured as R packages
Version: 0.4.1
Date: 2020-01-05
Authors@R: c(person("Francisco", "Rodriguez-Sanchez", email = "f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Mohamed Nadhir", "Djekidel", role="ctb"))
Description: This package works as a template for new research
    projects, under the idea of having everything (data, R scripts, functions
    and manuscript/reports) contained in the same package (a 'research compendium')
    to facilitate collaboration and promote reproducibility.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: CC0
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/Pakillo/template
BugReports: https://github.com/Pakillo/template/issues
Imports:
    devtools
Suggests:
    rmdTemplates,
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
